        </head>
        <body>
            <div class="lang-switch">
                <a class="active" href="index.html">中文</a>
                <span>/</span>
                <a href="index_en.html">EN</a>
            </div>
            <a class="nordic-logo" href="../index_zh.html">
                <img src="../assets/logo.png" alt="OceanBase" class="nordic-logo-img">
                <span class="nordic-logo-name">OceanBase</span>
                <span class="nordic-logo-text">OB × LangChain</span>
            </a>
            <div class="reveal">
                <div class="slides">
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 1 · Cover ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-hero text-center" style="max-width:860px;">
                            <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;line-height:1.1;">OceanBase × LangChain</h1>
                            <p class="slide-subtitle" style="margin:1.2rem auto 0;max-width:600px;">向量检索与混合搜索集成实战<br>从 pyobvector SDK 到生产级 RAG 管线</p>
                            <div style="width:48px;height:3px;background:var(--ob-blue);border-radius:2px;margin:2rem 0 1.5rem;"></div>
                            <div class="author-block" style="align-items:center;margin-top:0;">
                                <div class="author-name">OceanBase DevRel</div>
                                <div class="author-meta">Developer Relations @ OceanBase</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">开场：介绍 OceanBase 与 LangChain 生态的集成，目标听众为 AI 应用开发者。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 2 · Why OceanBase for AI ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">背景</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">为什么 AI 应用需要 OceanBase？</h2>
                        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-database-2-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> 数据孤岛爆炸</strong>
                                <p>向量、JSON、全文、GIS 分散在多个引擎，开发者被迫拼装 MySQL + ES + Pinecone 的"弗兰肯斯坦"架构。</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-refresh-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> 新鲜度 vs 规模</strong>
                                <p>传统向量库"最终一致性"导致 RAG 结果过时；OceanBase 严格 ACID 保证写入即可查。</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> 胶水代码税</strong>
                                <p>合并 MySQL + ES + Vector DB 结果需要 500+ 行 Python；OceanBase 一条 SQL 完成混合检索。</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-tools-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> 运维疲劳</strong>
                                <p>多套集群、多种 API、多种故障模式——AI 应用不该这么复杂。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">痛点：数据孤岛、一致性、胶水代码、运维复杂度。OceanBase 用一个引擎解决所有问题。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 3 · OceanBase Vector Capabilities ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">能力</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">OceanBase 向量能力一览</h2>
                        <div class="feature-grid" style="margin-top:1.2rem;">
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-search-eye-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);"></i></div>
                                <h4>向量存储 & 索引</h4>
                                <p>VECTOR 类型 + HNSW 索引，支持 L2 / Inner Product / Cosine 距离</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-file-search-line" style="color:var(--ob-teal);"></i></div>
                                <h4>全文检索</h4>
                                <p>内置 FULLTEXT 索引，无需 Elasticsearch 外挂</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-git-merge-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);"></i></div>
                                <h4>混合搜索</h4>
                                <p>DBMS_HYBRID_SEARCH 包：向量 + 全文 + 标量过滤，单查询完成</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-shield-check-line" style="color:var(--ob-teal);"></i></div>
                                <h4>ACID 事务</h4>
                                <p>标量、向量、全文索引原子更新，零不一致窗口</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-braces-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);"></i></div>
                                <h4>JSON & GIS</h4>
                                <p>半结构化与空间数据统一存储，一个引擎覆盖全模态</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon"><i class="ri-plug-line" style="color:var(--ob-teal);"></i></div>
                                <h4>MySQL 兼容</h4>
                                <p>现有应用零改造迁移，保留完整 SQL 能力</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">OceanBase V4.3.3+ 原生支持向量类型和 HNSW 索引。核心优势：一个引擎搞定所有。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 4 · pyobvector SDK ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">SDK</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">pyobvector — Python SDK 两种模式</h2>
                        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1.2rem;">
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-api-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> Milvus 兼容模式</strong>
                                <p>MilvusLikeClient 类，API 与 Milvus 对齐，迁移零成本。</p>
                                <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
                                    <div class="code-block-title">Python</div>
                                    <pre><code class="language-python">from pyobvector import MilvusLikeClient
        
        client = MilvusLikeClient(
            uri="127.0.0.1:2881",
            user="root@test"
        )
        # 创建集合 + 向量索引
        client.create_collection(
            collection_name="docs",
            schema=schema,
            index_params=idx_params,
        )</code></pre>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-database-line" style="color:var(--ob-teal);margin-right:4px;"></i> SQLAlchemy 混合模式</strong>
                                <p>ObVecClient 类，向量操作 + SQL 查询一体化，扩展 SQLAlchemy。</p>
                                <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
                                    <div class="code-block-title">Python</div>
                                    <pre><code class="language-python">from pyobvector import ObVecClient
        from sqlalchemy import func
        
        client = ObVecClient(
            uri="127.0.0.1:2881",
            user="root@test"
        )
        # ANN 搜索 + 标量过滤
        res = client.ann_search(
            table_name="docs",
            vec_data=embedding,
            vec_column_name="embedding",
            distance_func=func.l2_distance,
            topk=5,
        )</code></pre>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">pyobvector 提供两种模式：Milvus 兼容（迁移友好）和 SQLAlchemy 混合（灵活查询）。安装：pip install pyobvector</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 5 · LangChain Integration ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">集成</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">langchain-oceanbase — LangChain VectorStore</h2>
                        <div class="step-list" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">01</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>安装依赖</strong>
                                    <p><code>pip install langchain-oceanbase pyobvector</code></p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">02</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>初始化 OceanBaseVectorStore</strong>
                                    <p>传入 Embedding 模型 + 数据库连接，自动建表建索引</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">03</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>添加文档</strong>
                                    <p><code>vectorstore.add_documents(docs)</code> — 自动分块、嵌入、入库</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">04</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>混合检索</strong>
                                    <p>向量相似度 + 全文检索 + 标量过滤，可配置权重融合</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="code-block-title">Python</div>
                            <pre><code class="language-python">from langchain_oceanbase import OceanBaseVectorStore
        from langchain_openai import OpenAIEmbeddings
        
        vs = OceanBaseVectorStore(
            embedding=OpenAIEmbeddings(),
            connection_args={
                "host": "127.0.0.1", "port": "2881",
                "user": "root@test", "password": "",
                "database": "test"
            },
        )
        
        # 添加文档
        vs.add_documents(split_docs)
        
        # 混合搜索
        results = vs.similarity_search(
            "OceanBase 分布式架构", k=5
        )</code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">langchain-oceanbase v0.3.3 已发布到 PyPI，支持 Hybrid Search 和元数据过滤。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 6 · RAG Pipeline ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">RAG</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">端到端 RAG 管线</h2>
                        <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-file-text-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> 文档摄入</strong>
                                <p>LangChain DocumentLoader → TextSplitter → Embeddings → OceanBaseVectorStore</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-search-line" style="color:var(--ob-teal);margin-right:4px;"></i> 混合检索</strong>
                                <p>用户 Query → Embedding → 向量 + 全文混合搜索 → DBMS_HYBRID_SEARCH 加权融合</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-robot-line" style="color:var(--ob-blue);margin-right:4px;"></i> 生成回答</strong>
                                <p>Retriever → Context 拼接 → LLM (GPT-4 / Qwen / DeepSeek) → 结构化输出</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="callout">
                                <strong><i class="ri-loop-left-line" style="color:var(--ob-teal);margin-right:4px;"></i> 评估迭代</strong>
                                <p>LangSmith / RAGAS 评估 → 调整 chunk 大小、检索权重、reranker 策略</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="code-block-title">Python — RAG Chain</div>
                            <pre><code class="language-python">from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser
        from langchain_core.runnables import RunnablePassthrough
        from langchain_openai import ChatOpenAI
        
        retriever = vs.as_retriever(search_kwargs={"k": 5})
        llm = ChatOpenAI(model="gpt-4o")
        
        rag_chain = (
            {"context": retriever | format_docs, "question": RunnablePassthrough()}
            | prompt
            | llm
            | StrOutputParser()
        )
        
        rag_chain.invoke("OceanBase 如何实现分布式一致性？")</code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">完整的 RAG 管线：加载文档 → 分块 → 嵌入 → 存储 → 检索 → 生成。OceanBase 作为 VectorStore 替代 Pinecone/Weaviate。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 7 · Hybrid Search Deep Dive ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">混合搜索</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">DBMS_HYBRID_SEARCH 深度解析</h2>
                        <div class="step-list" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">01</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>标量过滤</strong>
                                    <p>WHERE 条件先缩小范围，从百万级到千级</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">02</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>粗排：向量 + 全文</strong>
                                    <p>HNSW 向量近邻 + FULLTEXT 关键词匹配，低成本并行召回</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-item">
                                <span class="step-num">03</span>
                                <div class="step-content">
                                    <strong>精排：Reranker</strong>
                                    <p>高精度重排序，可配置向量/全文权重比</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="code-block-title">SQL — 混合搜索</div>
                            <pre><code class="language-sql">CALL DBMS_HYBRID_SEARCH(
          table_name   => 'knowledge_base',
          query_text   => '分布式事务一致性协议',
          vector_col   => 'embedding',
          fulltext_col => 'content',
          top_k        => 10,
          alpha        => 0.7   -- 向量权重 0.7, 全文权重 0.3
        );</code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">alpha 参数控制向量与全文的权重。0.7 表示 70% 语义相似度 + 30% 关键词匹配。可根据场景调整。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 8 · Comparison Table ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">对比</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">架构对比：为什么选择 OceanBase？</h2>
                        <table style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th style="width:22%;">特性</th>
                                    <th style="width:26%;">经典方案<br><small>SQL + ES + Vector DB</small></th>
                                    <th style="width:26%;">专用方案<br><small>SQL + Pinecone</small></th>
                                    <th style="width:26%;background:var(--ob-blue-10);">OceanBase<br><small>统一引擎</small></th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>系统数量</strong></td>
                                    <td>3 套</td>
                                    <td>2 套</td>
                                    <td style="background:var(--ob-blue-10);"><strong>1 套</strong></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>数据一致性</strong></td>
                                    <td>弱 / 最终一致</td>
                                    <td>无事务保证</td>
                                    <td style="background:var(--ob-blue-10);"><strong>严格 ACID</strong></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>搜索能力</strong></td>
                                    <td>全文强，向量弱</td>
                                    <td>向量强，全文弱</td>
                                    <td style="background:var(--ob-blue-10);"><strong>向量 + 全文 + 标量</strong></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>开发体验</strong></td>
                                    <td>3x 运维 + 同步调试</td>
                                    <td>大量胶水代码</td>
                                    <td style="background:var(--ob-blue-10);"><strong>SQL 原生，零胶水</strong></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>MySQL 兼容</strong></td>
                                    <td>部分</td>
                                    <td>否</td>
                                    <td style="background:var(--ob-blue-10);"><strong>完全兼容</strong></td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                        <aside class="notes">核心卖点：一个引擎替代三个系统，严格 ACID，SQL 原生混合搜索。</aside>
                    </section>
        
                    <!-- ══ Slide 9 · Quick Start ══ -->
                    <section data-background-color="#fafafa">
                        <div class="slide-label"><span class="pill">快速开始</span></div>
                        <h2 class="slide-title">5 分钟上手</h2>
                        <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:1rem;">
                            <div class="code-block-title">Shell — Docker 启动 OceanBase</div>
                            <pre><code class="language-bash"># 启动 OceanBase CE (向量能力需 V4.3.3+)
        docker run -d --name ob \
          -p 2881:2881 \
          -e OB_MEMORY_LIMIT=6G \
          oceanbase/oceanbase-ce:4.3.5-lts</code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
                            <div class="code-block-title">Shell — 安装 & 运行</div>
                            <pre><code class="language-bash">pip install langchain-oceanbase pyobvector langchain-openai
        
        # 或使用 seekdb 轻量版
        docker run -d --name seekdb \
          -p 2881:2881 -p 2886:2886 \
          -v ./seekdb:/var/lib/oceanbase \
          oceanbase/seekdb:latest</code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-block" style="margin-top:0.6rem;">
                            <div class="code-block-title">Python — 最小 RAG 示例</div>
                            <pre><code class="language-python">from langchain_oceanbase import OceanBaseVectorStore
        from langchain_openai import OpenAIEmbeddings, ChatOpenAI
        
        vs = OceanBaseVectorStore(
            embedding=OpenAIEmbeddings(),
            connection_args={"host":"127.0.0.1","port":"2881",
                             "user":"root@test","database":"test"},
        )
        vs.add_texts(["OceanBase 是分布式关系数据库"])
        print(vs.similarity_search("什么是 OceanBase?", k=1))</code></pre>
                        </div>
                        <aside class="notes">三步即可运行：1) Docker 启动 OB 2) pip install 3) Python 代码连接。seekdb 更轻量，1C2G 即可运行。</aside>
                    </section>
        
